<div class="ss">
<h2>Shrook</h2>


<img id="screenshot" alt="Shrook 2 screenshot" src="http://www.fondantfancies.com/images/shrook/screenshot2.gif" width="512" height="324" />

<h3>The RSS reader that syncs</h3>

<p>Shrook is a full-featured RSS reader that's completely free - no ads, no spyware. And if you want to access your feeds on another Mac, iPhone or any web-connected PC, just get a shrook.com account for painless synchronization.</p>

</div>

<div>

